com.legacy.structure_gel.util

Class RegistryHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.legacy.structure_gel.util.RegistryHelper

  • public class RegistryHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple class that gives methods to ease the registry process by a bit. Note: As of 1.16.2, jigsaw structures no longer require a piece type.
    Author:
    David
